{"tid":701181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女友聲稱被強姦　男警涉案重案調查","createTime":"2018-06-14T02:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T09:15:25.000Z","uid":116054,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"adf2703b254607f5b84c33f5a80f5b19931e21e9","tid":701181,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"女友聲稱被強姦　男警涉案重案調查<br />\n<br />\n一名女子昨日(12日)報案，聲稱遭一名男子強姦。據悉，涉案男子為一名警員，駐守黃大仙警區，港島總區重案組接手跟進。至今日（13日），重案組探員到黃大仙警署，向涉案男警了解事件經過。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，涉案男警已婚，早前結識女事主並發展感情，雙方曾發生性關係，惟女事主事後卻聲稱在不願意的情況下，與人發生性行為，遂報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，在6月12日接獲一名33歲女子報案，案件暫列作「求警調查」，由港島總區重案組接手調查，暫未有人被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n休班強姦犯一定又係無罪釋放，分都費事加！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180613/mobile/bkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180613%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001.html&d=jSaVrvWmoXwvmhgKSppV0%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ad3c3c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180613/mobile/bkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6a1530edfbb9431e452a222abec76d44fd4f6f43","tid":701181,"uid":35453,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"奴"},{"pid":"04db51707b6296ae10e5feba7d1f5ec74f9cdda3","tid":701181,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"又"},{"pid":"5cb2dde908c4d114d0580bc8f74f5c94e7916b65","tid":701181,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:08:43.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b7c594fb7ca67e190c2a6731bb8ecd3f97ea4c","tid":701181,"uid":143454,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d74293b030bbac5e61c4a57c26836600afeb5cf","tid":701181,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"cite